  "keyFeatures": [
    "Ontology-driven data modeling with OWL/Turtle support",
    "Multi-backend storage (PostgreSQL, MySQL, MongoDB, S3, Redis, Elasticsearch, Neo4j)",
    "Pipeline-based data ingestion and processing",
    "ML model training and inference (Decision Trees, Random Forest, Regression, Neural Networks)",
    "Digital twin management with SPARQL query engine",
    "Model Context Protocol (MCP) integration with 55 tools for AI agents",
    "Kubernetes-native worker execution",
    "Common Internal Representation (CIR) for unified data format"
